<p class="updated">Last updated: February 13, 2026</p>
<h2>Overview</h2><p>Vibe Tutor is a personalized AI-powered learning assistant designed for children with ADHD, Autism Spectrum, and ODD. We take your child's privacy seriously.</p>
<h2>Data We Collect</h2><ul><li><strong>Chat Messages:</strong> Processed in real-time for educational responses. <strong>Not stored permanently</strong> — only held in memory during an active session.</li><li><strong>Session Tokens:</strong> Temporary, anonymous tokens that expire after 24 hours. They do not identify the user.</li><li><strong>Analytics Events:</strong> Lightweight, anonymous usage data to improve the app. No PII included.</li></ul>
